# Licensing

This repository is dual-licensed by content type:

- **Textual content** — recipes, planning notes, meal plans, documentation, and
  all other prose and Markdown — is released under the **Creative Commons CC0
  1.0 Universal** public-domain dedication. No rights reserved, no attribution
  required. See [`LICENSE-CC0.txt`](LICENSE-CC0.txt).

- **Code** — scripts and any other software in this repository (e.g. everything
  under [`scripts/`](scripts/)) — is licensed under the **MIT License**. See
  [`LICENSE-MIT.txt`](LICENSE-MIT.txt).

Committed images are textual-content-adjacent assets and fall under CC0 to the
extent the contributors hold rights in them. Recipes validated against external
sources reflect facts and techniques (not copyrightable) rewritten in our own
words; the original sources retain their own rights to their own expression.
